{
  "texts": [
    "The formulation of Scheme 2 is illustrated via Eqs.",
    "(3)-(6).",
    "The f sp (⋅) is used to decompose the input into m subseries s 1, s 2, …, s m.",
    "The i th subseries is processed using the corresponding feature engineering component f fe i (⋅).",
    "As in Scheme 1, optionally, all of the feature engineering components can also be optimized via f o (⋅) in Scheme 2."
  ]
}